body.name: Keep Connect Router Wi-Fi Reset Device. Automatic Router Rebooter. If You Enter a Phone Number it Will Send Texts Upon resets.
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Friday, February 16. Order within 11 hrs 28 mins
features: Automatic Router Rebooter - Stop manually rebooting your router and let Keep Connect automate the process. Keep Connect will constantly monitor your internet health and automatically reboots your router or modem when disconnected. You can also choose to receive notifications through email or SMS if you enter your phone number.

Ensures a Reliable Internet Connection 24/7/365 - Keep Connect will make sure your connected devices are always online and available. You can also Schedule Periodic Resets to keep your connection fresh and fast.

Compact Size - Keep Connect’s smaller size makes it a perfect fit for your receptacle space, making it an ideal choice for apartments, small homes, or any space where you need reliable internet connectivity without taking up too much space. Perfect use for your Smart Home, Office, Business, or Remote Locations.

Premium Cloud Services App Available (iOS App Store and Google Play Store) - Our Premium Keep Connect Cloud Services platform allows using our Online/Mobile App to monitor many locations in one place as well. Cloud Services allows remote management of devices at all locations as well as heartbeat monitoring of your Keep Connects to notify you in the event of an ISP internet outage at one of your sites.

Industry-leading Customer Service - Our team is dedicated to providing you with top-notch customer service and technical support. Whether you have questions, need assistance, or require troubleshooting, our support team is available to help you every step of the way.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Always Connected! Always Online! Keep Connect will Constantly Monitor Your Connection to Ensure that Your Assets are Always Available! Stop spending your time rebooting your router and let us do the work to make sure your connection is always available. Perfect for Smart Homes - Keep all of your Connected Devices (Home Security, Smart Thermostats, Door Locks, Leak Sensors, etc.) OnlineAutomatic Reboots - Constantly monitors internet connection 24/7/365 and issues reboots whenever failure is detected.Scheduled Reboots - Use our Auto Reset feature to schedule reboots at a fixed interval to ensure fresh connections and router/modem software cachesSMS/Email Notifications - Enable SMS/Email Notifications to stay in the know with how Keep Connect is performing on your networkSimple, Yet Configurable - Our out-of-the-box configuration works great for most users. If you're a more advanced user or have a custom application, there are many user configurable settings to adjust nearly all aspects of operations from timing intervals, scheduled reboot periods, monitoring modes, etc.Master/Follower Coordinated Reboots - You can coordinate multiple units to communicate and reboot together for applications where you would like to reboot a router and modem simultaneously while then bringing the modem back online before the router.No App Needed - All setup and configuration is done without requiring an app. Just connect to Keep Connect's WiFi SSID (similar to connecting to airport/public WiFi) to trigger an auto-launch configuration page to get you up and running quickly.Subscription Based Cloud Monitoring Available - Our Keep Connect Cloud Services Platform (sold separately) allows monitoring and control of many devices at different locations all from within one place. We offer an iOS/Android app and also a browser based web app. Our Keep Connect Cloud Services Platform will even monitor heartbeats from your Keep Connect units and send you notifications if any Keep Connect becomes unreachable due to an Internet Service Provider (ISP) outage or similar event.

Keep Connect Cloud Services Platform (sold separately) Global Access and Control of All Your Keep Connect Units Remote MonitoringRemote ControlRemote AdministrationAll In One PlaceAvailable on iOS and Android or within Browser Web App

Residential/Vacation Home Use Keep your internet online and all of your devices connected both at your primary residence as well as at your vacation homes that may be located far away from you. Rental Homes and Properties Keep your tenants and vacation renters online and minimize maintenance and help desk requests when the solution is as simple as power cycling the router or modem. Office Buildings and Workplace Keep your workplace connected and online to maximize productivity in today's connected world. Minimize downtime and inefficiency by allowing Keep Connect to do all of your router reboot work. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worked for what i needed but....
reviews.reviewText: This reset my router every time I had a wifi outage and worked great. But my problem is deeper than just rebooting, so yes this worked in finding I need a deeper resolution to my problem. It worked so well my router was rebooting every hour, so deeper issue with my problem. Very easy setup but there is a lot of optional setup that is beyond me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Effortless daily reboots- a must for T-Mobile Home Internet
reviews.reviewText: The daily reboots work as expected, and any time the Internet cuts out I can sit back and let KeepConnect do the work to restart my routerThe unexpected benefit is my T-Mobile Home Internet download speeds are now a lot faster: 10 Mbps have improved to 40 Mbps. I guess the TMHI router firmware can't handle long uptimes.I've had it for a month and am very happy with the performance. The one-time setup is a bit fiddly, so if you're not tech savvy, ask for help. You have to connect to the plug as if it were a separate WiFi network. I set mine to reboot every night at 4am, and check for connection every 2 minutes. All other settings I left as default.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We are in a rural area with internet that can be pretty flaky, and this thing is incredibly useful. The set-up was easy, it does its job with no fuss, and now no one has to yell across the house to reboot the router/modem. Thumbs up!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not as easy as plug and play
reviews.reviewText: It sounded like we should plug the router into it and all is good. Unfortunately it doesn’t work that way. My daughter went to our winter home and it can’t be set up without our phones/accounts there. Disappointed, hopefully in 4 months we can get it to work when we return.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Finally a Simple Solution
reviews.reviewText: Very effective device and vital for anyone who needs to reboot their router to restore service. Instructions could be a little clearer in terms of the web based configuration, but even someone with little technical experience can figure it out. The default settings are a little too sensitive for my house, so I ran it a few days to optimize just how sensitive it should be before rebooting. The first day it was plugged in, it rebooted my router during a Zoom conference, so you may need to adjust it so that it really needs multiple outages for long periods before it reboot. Regardless, I’m far less worried about my router locking up and my cameras being inaccessible when I’m away from home. Get one today!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I didn’t know this device existed!!
reviews.reviewText: I have T-mobile home internet, which is very glitchy. I constantly need to reboot it just so I can get decent speed, but only when I’m home. A lot of times, I can’t access my security cameras/thermostat remotely because my wifi is acting up. But nothing I can do since I’m not home to reboot my router. I just came across this device which I didn’t know even existed!! It reboots my router automatically and I can even set it to reboot on schedule. You can also have it notify you by text or email when it does a reboot. and it’s easy to install. I haven’t had it that long but it’s working very well. There is an older version of this device which I think is oversized. I got the newer one which is smaller and more compact. It does not block the other outlets. At $50, it is a little pricey though. And if you want their online cloud service, that’s another $25 a year. I wish the $50 includes one year of cloud service. Other than that, it’s a great product!! Will post updates if anything changes

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It reboots things!
reviews.reviewText: What can I say? It does what it says it does, and does it reliably! I have a T-Mobile home internet router. If you leave it on continuously, it will occasionally slow down and need a reboot. I've set this up to reboot the router at 4am every other day. It dutifully does so, then sends me a text message.Setup was quick using the app. There is an upsell for some extra features, but you really don't need them.Simple as that!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We tried the setup many times, but the device never connected to our Netgear router. The device does not appear in the WIFI selections, nor does 192.168.4.1 does not find the setup page.

I’ve been looking for a device like this for years and it worked exactly as I would hope. I have two properties 325km apart, on occasion I would experience an internet outage, more so lately after switching my home to Bell Fibre. Internet outages would always happen at one place when I was at the other. In the last 2 weeks my home lost internet 5 times, this device reset my Bell modem and everything was up and running in minutes. I no longer have rely on friends and family to reset my modems, when I’m away. I have one internet rebooter at each location, I now have confidence both location will have a stable internet connection. Great product.
Works great in rebooting router. My internet drops out at 5am most weeks. Cable company has tries but can't trouble shoot reason. This works wonderfully.

reviews.reviewTitle: It works well and has several useful options
reviews.reviewText: After trying an Ankuoo auto switch which kept going into a loop as the delay to wait for full reboot was set too short and was not adjustable, making it useless, this unit works perfectly!The setup is simple. If you want to test the unit to see if it works, do NOT change the default settings. If you set a check time other than 5 minutes, it does not work. This minor problem has been solved in the new firmware. My unit came with firmware KeepConnect_KCMINI_4M_V3_Rev2 and I upgraded it to the latest KeepConnectVPN_KCMINI_4M_V4_Rev1. You need to send an email to support to get the link for the new firmware.I tested it several times and it worked each time.You can also have it programmed to reset your modem once a day, every 2nd day, every 3rd day etc... I have not tested that part, as I don't need to do this, but I don't see why it would not work.It is also much smaller than their former model which is a plus.Overall I do recommend this little unit: it does what it is supposed to do!
IT's been a long while I've been looking for a budget solution for hands free router restart, this on does the job perfectly while fitting the budget. Thank you !!!
